Hiya,

Topic: Inter Process Communication (IPC) using Semaphores
Compile: gcc ipc_semapohore.c -lpthread -o ipc_semapohore
Instructions to run:
  1. Run the ipc_semaphore binary (./ipc_semaphore).
  2. Enter the number of children processes (eg: 10).
  3. Enter the number of semaphore (resources) (eg: 2).
